  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TKT19">
<l>piṇṭiyār maṇṭai yēntip piṟarmaṉai tiritan tuṇṇum</l>
<l>muṇṭiyāṉ cāpan tīrtta voruvaṉū rulaka mēttum</l>
<l>kaṇṭiyū raraṅkam meyyaṅ kaccipēr mallai yeṉṟu</l>
<l>maṇṭiṉā ruyya lallāl maṟṟaiyārk kuyya lāmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The cities of the one who ended the curse of the beggar -</l>
<l>[The one] who, bearing a skull full of offerings, ate, being made to wander to others’ houses -</l>
<l>Are Kaṇṭiyūr, Araṅkam, Meyyam, Kacci, Pēr, and Mallai which are praised in the world;</l>
<l>Besides the salvation of those who throng [there], is there salvation for [any] others?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
